{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"57dea7cb74","title":"勤俭请从首都做起 (杂文)","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a62e0f159f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"57dea7cb74"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3aae6e8366","name":"中共中央高级党校"},{"id":"de0adac7c8","name":"姚北桦"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d28b26b81a","type":"title","text":"勤俭请从首都做起(杂文)","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"f8895f4e23","type":"authors","text":"中共中央高级党校姚北桦","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"0afde95989","type":"paragraph","text":"（姚北桦：新闻班第三班第一支部学员；入学前为江苏《新华日报》副刊主编）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"37b5d7c66c","type":"paragraph","text":"[原编者按：这是在1957年3、4月间草拟的一篇杂文的提纲。反右派斗争中自己交出。下面是它的全文。]","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"f90f066deb","type":"paragraph","text":"北京人的幸福、光荣。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"d02b8fec2f","type":"paragraph","text":"但北京人的责任也就特别重大。——全国人民都看着北京，以北京人做自己的楷模。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"21825e53d8","type":"paragraph","text":"因而，我有一个提议，就是勤俭请从北京做起。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"888eaa5ed0","type":"paragraph","text":"这样说，并不是说北京人特别浪费和奢侈，因此北京人要特别注意勤俭。不，请不要误会。我只是说，北京人如果能够在勤俭建国方面做出榜样，那么影响一定会遍及全国。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"4088bec5e8","type":"paragraph","text":"何况，在现实生活中，北京有一些风气，也不是不应当改变的呢！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"dc580831d4","type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个来北京不久的人。把外地生活和北京比较一下，我就有这样一些感觉。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"6295f72f97","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）穿着布衣服的人来北京，就好象很寒蠢，这儿的服装，非呢不可。（舞会）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"0b9de0711a","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）建筑——（剧场、厕所、宿舍、喷水池、座位）农村开会。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"be2fb5e733","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）节约用电（舞会）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"a8f5006795","type":"paragraph","text":"批判几种说法：","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"66866a2d68","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）生活水平不同谈。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"eb3e177fdf","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）国际观瞻所系说。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"6731e76fb8","type":"paragraph","text":"你的说法片面！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"},{"id":"eaf73f1276","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：中共中央高级党校校部办公室印；共印1800份，发全校学员和有关干部。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74"}],"page":{"id":"9711964ae9","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"57dea7cb74","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}